sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer (User)
    participant UI as UiPath Apps (Dashboard)
    participant Maestro as UiPath Maestro (BPMN)
    participant Agent as Coding Agent (Cursor/Claude)
    participant Memory as UiPath Data Service (Master Memory)
    participant Lead as Senior Developer (Human-in-the-loop)

    Dev->>UI: Submit coding task request
    UI->>Maestro: Trigger BPMN Process (Task: "Feature X")
    Maestro->>Memory: Retrieve "Code Soul" & "Minefield History"
    Maestro->>Agent: Assign Phase-0 Alignment Interview
    
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        note right of Maestro: Phase-0 Alignment (Governance)
        Agent->>Agent: Analyze requirements against Minefield
        Agent-->>Maestro: Propose Implementation Plan
    end

    Maestro->>Lead: Create Task in UiPath Action Center
    Lead->>Lead: Review Plan vs Code Soul
    
    alt Plan Rejected
        Lead-->>Maestro: Reject with feedback
        Maestro->>Memory: Update Minefield History (Add failed pattern)
        Maestro->>Agent: Re-assign Phase-0 with new feedback
    else Plan Approved
        Lead-->>Maestro: Approve Implementation
        Maestro->>Agent: Grant execution permission
        Agent->>Agent: Write Code (Execution Phase)
        Agent-->>Maestro: Code completion signal
        Maestro->>Memory: Update State Memory (Task completed)
    end
    
    Maestro-->>UI: Notify Developer (Task Finished)
